{"tid":2228883,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［黃色經濟圈］樂文 紙漫糖 內訌","createTime":"2020-10-04T03:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T12:35:25.000Z","uid":84308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4e10d13588a0a188b0100b52f607b73e4d6e5980","tid":2228883,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T03:18:58.000Z","msg":"事源facebook有人咁講：<br />\n<br />\n「樂文玩具公司偷人設計拎去買事件:<br />\n<br />\n其實上年大家一直有整嘅立體連豬紙模係紙波糖設計嘅，今年中秋佢設計咗個連豬燈籠免費比大家下載，而且為不便的人提供代印服務$20<br />\n<br />\n但樂文就無問過紙漫糖就拎咗人地設計去賣，仲要每個賣$38，賣貴人成倍<br />\n<br />\n因為紙漫糖一直有同其他黃店合作，亦都會幫合作伙伴宣傳，但佢就從未提及有同樂文有合作<br />\n<br />\n我就好奇去樂文質問有冇經紙漫糖同意先賣，佢就一直迴避問題，而且佢經我質問先死死地氣不情願地加 鳴謝字眼。<br />\n<br />\n我出呢個po冇經紙漫糖同意，如果佢要求我會del po，我出呢個po亦唔係想批鬥樂文，只係希望大家尊重創作，雖然紙漫糖係做二次創作，但創作背後都要時間心血<br />\n<br />\n希望大家尊重返創作人，如果要銷售要問返創作者，就算對方同意亦都要鳴謝對方，互相合作先可以長遠發展」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2586212984760547/permalink/3363078490407322/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F2586212984760547%2Fpermalink%2F3363078490407322%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=b147a3d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/2586212984760547/permalink/3363078490407322/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GExzvq5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGExzvq5.jpg&h=3e01497c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n創作者咁樣講：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UBFEGxS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUBFEGxS.png&h=c2af135a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事態發展：<br />\n紙漫糖被屌跣樂文一獲 黃絲質問紙漫糖過去作品無credit過lihkg 亦唔算得係咩創作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a427QtJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa427QtJ.png&h=44b602ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/118691898283454/posts/1767816440037650/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F118691898283454%2Fposts%2F1767816440037650%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=93c3f905\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/118691898283454/posts/1767816440037650/</a>"},{"pid":"3287362449ad65ca2ace63999bdcb5601c78b1eb","tid":2228883,"uid":41812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:33:13.000Z","msg":"推，冇人討論"},{"pid":"48f50a1aab334dc2199668193e045828728fe4b7","tid":2228883,"uid":41812,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:34:32.000Z","msg":"其實你同嗰班人傾冇得傾，佢哋根本唔知乜係二次創作<br />\n討論都應該要同咁上下知識水平嘅人先討論得到"},{"pid":"9a0735b4541b9cee775e6aef0507345555524d79","tid":2228883,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:38:12.000Z","msg":"屌咩柒都話黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但又冇咩證據係黃<br />\n<br />\n已經唔想理  <br />\n<br />\n只信蕭生  咁多年冇停過撚化老人<br />\n<br />\n真黃"},{"pid":"50a5cf8333c6ad64ba2829bbba10b0da5e7a3e9b","tid":2228883,"uid":97,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:35:25.000Z","msg":"唔係龍門同渣哥 無人理嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}